pageContext.claim: “Washington Examiner – ‘MAGA list: 205 “historic results” help Trump make case for 2020 re-election.’  True!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is tweeting out a list of 205 purported accomplishments from his administration. Although he's linking to the Washington Examiner, the list actually came from his own White House. His tweet makes it seem as if someone else came up with this list of 205 "historic results."
